<p>To <strong>fix the Base URL</strong>, follow the steps below:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Enter the <strong>MySQLi data</strong> using <strong>phpMyAdmin</strong> (for example)</li>
  <li>Go to the table <strong>oc_config</strong></li>
  <li>Then search for general - <strong>base_url</strong></li>
  <li>Modify it and <strong>Save</strong> the data</li>
  <li><strong>Delete cache</strong> by deleting the contents of folder /oc/cache/*</li>
</ol>

<p>That should work!</p>

